[p 
	"Star Control II is one of the greatest PC games ever. It is a space
	$LF
	"adventure/exploration game that has a story, battles, exploration,
	$LF
	"thousands of worlds to mine, and a modular flagship that can be
	$LF
	"configured for whatever purpose needed.
	$LF
	"It sports a large number of different alien species, most of which can be encountered
	$LF
	"during the gameplay; some of which become allies, some of which become enemies, and
	$LF
	"some which become neither.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"There were literally hours of dialogue, each species bringing out their
	$LF
	"characteristic conversational quirks, music, and even display fonts. Almost a hour
	$LF
	"of digital music is also included.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Because you can pretty much go anywhere whenever you want, there is
	$LF
	"no "sequence breaking" in this game. However, there are numerous things
	$LF
	"that are required for the game to be completed.
