[p 
	"This speedrun attempts to complete the game in a minimal amount of time,
	$LF
	"and the completion time ends up being 35:04.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"It is the first DOS tool-assisted speedrun on this site. Although the method
	$LF
	"used to create it was not as robust as for the console game speedruns so far,
	$LF
	"it is still a legitimate TAS nonetheless, with savestates and frame advance
	$LF
	"being used and no file edit/TSR hacks.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Because it is rather unlikely anyone will be able to replay the actual
	$LF
	"movie file, given the myriad of ways the game installation or DOSBox
	$LF
	"configuration may differ, an AVI was submitted together with the movie file.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" To playback this movie
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"You need to have:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" A registered copy of Star Control II game
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" Ensure that the following files are present: androsyn.shp arilou.shp blackurq.shp chenjesu.shp chmmr.shp druuge.shp human.shp ilwrath.shp melnorme.shp mmrnmhrm.shp mycon.shp orz.shp pkunk.shp shofixti.shp slylandr.shp spathi.shp supox.shp syreen.shp thradd.shp umgah.shp urquan.shp utwig.shp vux.shp yehat.shp zoqfot.shp con1.pkg con2.pkg ip.pkg melee.pkg setup.pkg starcon.pkg starcon2.exe
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Ensure that a following file does 
				[em 
					"not
				]em
				" exist: starcon2.bat or starcon2.com
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Ensure that your version is not cracked. It must ask for a star name in the beginning, and not take enter for an answer. If there is a starcon2.exb, rename it to starcon2.exe.
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
		" A rerecording version of Dosbox
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" Take dosbox-0.70 source code, add 
				[a class=extlink href=http://bisqwit.iki.fi/src/patch-dosbox-0.70-rerecording-alpha3.gz rel=nofollow 
					"this patch
				]a
				" and compile it.
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Alternatively, take a precompiled Windows version from here: http://media.tasvideos.org/dosbox-rerecording-exe-a3.zip
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Hit F4 to unpause the emulator, to start the movie
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Numlock ON when you start the movie (otherwise, it does not type "2" properly).
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
		" The submitted dosbox.conf file and the submitted movie.dof file present in the game's directory
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	" Plot
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	[b 
		"SPOILERS
	]b
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This game has a 
	[em 
		"lot
	]em
	" of subplots, but here is the most important one.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[em 
		"Portions of this plot are actually supposed to be discovered from
		$LF
		"different sources throughout the playing, so if you intend to play
		$LF
		"this game, do not read this chapter.
		$LF
		"(Go 
		[a class=extlink href=http://sc2.sourceforge.net/ rel=nofollow 
			"here
		]a
		" to download a version
		$LF
		"of the game that works on modern operating systems.)
	]em
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The Ur-Quan are an ancient, proud and naturally xenophobic civilized alien species.
	$LF
	"Twenty thousand years ago, when they were already avid space travellers,
	$LF
	"they discovered a 
	[em 
		"talking pet
	]em
	", an animal of the species of Dnyarri
	$LF
	"resembling the cross between a toad and a mushroom.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This talking pet turned out to be a highly malevolent sentient creature
	$LF
	"that was capable of assuming complete mental control over other lifeforms.
	$LF
	"The single talking pet compelled the Ur-Quan to bring thousands of other
	$LF
	"Dnyarris to the Ur-Quan home planet, leading to the complete enslavement
	$LF
	"of the Ur-Quan species by the Dnyarri, for several thousands of years.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"During those times, the Ur-Quan species were split into two: the green,
	$LF
	"who were the thinkers, and the black, who were the warriors.
	$LF
	"They were forced to commit numerous atrocities around the galaxy,
	$LF
	"including the annihilation of the only other alien species they
	$LF
	"had ever considered a friend, the Taalo. Ironically, the Taalo, who were
	$LF
	"naturally immune to the mental control of the Dnyarri, were just in
	$LF
	"the process of finishing a device that would have granted freedom of
	$LF
	"that control to other races as well.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"One day, a green Ur-Quan scientist discovered that in the event of near-lethal pain
	$LF
	"to the Ur-Quan, the mental control by the talking pet was momentarily relieved.
	$LF
	"The word spread, and soon, all of the Ur-Quan were burning, hacking and poisoning
	$LF
	"themselves in order to gain the upper hand over the Dnyarri.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Once the Dnyarri were conquered, the Ur-Quan robbed them of sentience and
	$LF
	"assigned them into the role of translators -- a task they hated themselves.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The now two Ur-Quan species each developed doctrines to prevent such
	$LF
	"a catastrophic event ever happening again.
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" The doctrine of the green Ur-Quan (Kzer-Za), called "Path of Now And Forever", meant that all other sentient species must become either slaves to Ur-Quan ("battle-thralls") or be forever imprisoned on their homeworld under an impenetrable forcefield.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" The doctrine of the black Ur-Quan (Kohr-Ah), called "Eternal Doctrine", meant the entire annihilation of all other sentient species, so that they can only be reborn as Ur-Quan.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"Eventually, a war spawned between these two doctrines, and the green Ur-Quan
	$LF
	"came victorous through the discovery of an ancient weapon platform, the Sa-Matra.
	$LF
	"But the doctrines would meet again, and when that happens, whoever wins
	$LF
	"the Sa-Matra signifies the win of their doctrine as well.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The game starts at the time of that second conflict, and the black Ur-Quan, Kohr-Ah,
	$LF
	"seem to be winning. It is the task of the player to seek resolution to the problem,
	$LF
	"by ultimately destroying the Sa-Matra, with the help of the other alien species.
	$LF
	"Failing this task, the Kohr-Ah will eventually win the war (in about five years),
	$LF
	"and will start exterminating each and every alien species in the universe.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[b 
		"SPOILERS END HERE
	]b
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The player pilots an advanced precursor vessel found on a secret scientific
	$LF
	"mission in another solar system, and has quite missed everything that has
	$LF
	"happened recently, such as that Earth now has an inpenetrable force shield,
	$LF
	"as mandated by the Ur-Quan law.
	$LF
]p
