[p 
	"For many of the parts of the route, there are alternatives, so
	$LF
	"the game is not that linear. For example, besides having the Ilwrath
	$LF
	"attack the Thraddash, you can distract the Thraddash by allying them
	$LF
	"(requires destroying 25 of their ships in battle)
	$LF
	"and just "going to have a kind of look at the Aqua Helix",
	$LF
	"or by allying them and compelling them to go fight the Kohr-Ah. Or fourth,
	$LF
	"I could just wait until the Kohr-Ah slaughter the entire species when
	$LF
	"they start their ominous tour around the galaxy, but that would take
	$LF
	"five years of the game time.
	$LF
