[h4 
	" Route
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"This route mostly follows the speedrun walkthrough by lmfurb, available
	$LF
	"at !http://db.gamefaqs.com/computer/doswin/file/star_control_ii_speed.txt
	$LF
	"-- however, with a few changes.
	$LF
]p
[ol 
	[li 
		" Harvest Sol, equip ship. (160 fuel, max speed)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[b 
			"First trip
		]b
		" Travel to Alpha Pavonis to pick up a warp-pod from a crashed Ur-Quan ship.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Quasispace and deliver the warp-pod to Arilou. Receive portal spawner.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Arcturus and pick up the Burvixese caster.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Gamma Krueger and ally the Pkunk. Receive ships and Ultron part.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Alpha Taurii and trick the Ilwrath into attacking the Thraddash by impersonating their gods.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Sol, equip ship again. (160 fuel, Arilou+Pkunk+Earthling and max speed+fueltanks)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[b 
			"Second trip
		]b
		" Warp to Beta Copernicus and pick up a Mycon eggshell.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Epsilon Scorpii to receive some Mycon knowledge.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Betelgeuse and fury the Syreen whose former homeworld was destroyed by the Mycon.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Epsilon Cameleopardalis to get the Syreen some mobility.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Betelgeuse to learn about a plan to take revenge on the Mycon.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Delta Vulpeculae to befriend the Orz and to loot the Taalo shield.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Epsilon Scorpii, execute the captain's part of the revenge plan on Mycon.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Beta Brahe, attack (now weaker) Mycon and steal the Sun device.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Zeta Persei, purchase the Ultron part and a lot of fuel.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[b 
			"Third trip
		]b
		" Warp to Beta Orionis, get attacked by ten zombie Umgahs and pick up the Talking pet.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Zeta Draconis and steal the Ultron part.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Umgah/Supox space, get Ultron from Supox, fix it and give it to Utwig, making both allies.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Travel to Zeta Hyades, attack the Druuge and take the Bomb.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Warp to Procyon, flood the planet with energy and ally the resulting Chmmr.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Equip ship again.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" 
		[b 
			"Last trip
		]b
		" Warp to Delta Crateris, finish the destiny.
		$LF
	]li
]ol
[p 
	"The bolded "trips" mark the points where the fuel tank was refilled.
	$LF
]p
