[h3 
	" Auto-pilot strategy
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"The auto-pilot plots straighter courses than is possible to do oneself.
	$LF
	"In theory, it saves fuel and it saves time.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"However, while making this speedrun, I lost completely the confidence in
	$LF
	"the auto-pilot; I often found the manual steering to be faster (even when
	$LF
	"taking the map screen delays out of equation), and not consume noticeably
	$LF
	"more fuel than the auto-pilot does. It is unfortunate, because I would have
	$LF
	"liked to feature the mapscreen more, to give some idea where I'm going at
	$LF
	"a given time.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"I showed the mapscreen once right before entering the Delta Crateris system
	$LF
	"at the end, just for the show. It's not like this is the perfect movie if I
	$LF
	"left that out, and I think it's interesting to see.
	$LF
]p
[h3 
	" Questions and answers
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Q: What was the long wait for after acquiring the Urquan warppod?
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"A: The Quasispace portal appears between 17th and 20th days. I had a lot of
	$LF
	"slack time. However, I did not have slack fuel, so I couldn't move around.
	$LF
	"Also, I couldn't travel to the portal first, because the Arilou would have
	$LF
	"popped in and asked what I'm doing. Communications do not consume the timer.
	$LF
	"I could have equipped the ship with less speed upgrades... (and used the RU
	$LF
	"for ship rotation instead), but I believe this was faster in the end.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Q: At the first visit in the Mycon homeworld, why didn't you drive directly
	$LF
	"to the planet?
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"A: I wanted to get the attention of the patrolling Mycon ship, so that it
	$LF
	"comes closer instead of ambushing me when I try to leave the planet later.
	$LF
	"This prevented one fight. To get there to be only one Mycon ship in the first
	$LF
	"place, I luckmanipulated the entry to the solar system. The same was done at
	$LF
	"a few other places.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Q: That's it?
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"A: There were a lot of races we did not meet face-to-face in this speedrun --
	$LF
	"even of those which we battled with, such as Kohr-Ah and the Umgah -- and
	$LF
	"lots of subplots that were not visited. The Melnorme traders were never
	$LF
	"met, and hence, no alien beasts were collected on any planets.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Q: How much do you estimate this movie to be improveable?
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
